videos.headline: Rice QB fumbles snap in own end zone, UTEP jumps on it for TD
videos.description: Rice's Tom Stewart fumbles the snap in his own end zone, leaving UTEP's Praise Amaewhule to hop on the ball for a defensive touchdown.
